title: BsSndRpt expected argument 'i' ??
body:
everytime i lunch the game this massage apear i can't even see the luncher .. doesn't open !! 
please help

replies.body: nothing work here i have the same problem......

It sounds like there might be a corrupted file somewhere that is preventing the client from ever launching. Before we do a full reinstall, let's first try deleting LeagueClient.exe. Once you do that, when you try to launch the legacy client it should force a repatch. Once the repatch is finished, you should be able to get back into the game.

Let me know how this works for you!
